item.description:
 &lt;p&gt;翻译自：&lt;a href=&#34;https://askubuntu.com/a/1409732&#34;&gt;Answer to &amp;quot;Key is stored in legacy trusted.gpg keyring (/etc/apt/trusted.gpg)&amp;quot;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
