\frac{\partial V_\pi(s_t)}{\partial \boldsymbol \theta}&amp;amp;=
\mathbb E_{a \sim \pi}\left [ g(a) \right] \\
&amp;amp; \approx \frac{\partial \ln \pi(a_t\mid s_t;\boldsymbol \theta)}{\partial \boldsymbol \theta} Q_\pi(s_t, a_t) \\
&amp;amp; \approx \frac{\partial \ln \pi(a_t\mid s_t;\boldsymbol \theta)}{\partial \boldsymbol \theta} u_t
\end{aligned}
