= \mathbb E_{a \sim \pi}\left [ \frac{\partial \ln \pi(a\mid s_t;\boldsymbol \theta)}{\partial \boldsymbol \theta} [Q_\pi(s_t, a) - V^\star(s_t; \boldsymbol \omega)] \right ]
